# Modern Unix tools

[`bat` for `cat`](https://github.com/sharkdp/bat)

[`delta` for `git diff`](https://github.com/dandavison/delta)

[`eza` for `ls`](https://github.com/eza-community/eza)

[`ripgrep` for `grep`](https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep)

[`cheat`](https://github.com/cheat/cheat)

[`tldr`](https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr)

[`glances` replacement for`htop/btop`](https://github.com/nicolargo/glances)
